    bmi A function to read all available tabs from an excel file

    multi_import_excel.Rd

    bmi A function to read all available tabs from an excel file

    multi_import_excel(file = "inst/corrupted_toydatasets.xlsx")

    Arguments

    file

    the name or pathfile of the excel file (type = character)

    Value

    A list of data frames named after the excel tabs

    Examples

    file <- system.file("corrupted_toydatasets.xlsx", package = "annamantsoki")
multi_import_excel(file)
